Description: Portable command-line YAML, JSON, XML, CSV and properties processor
 yq is a lightweight and portable command-line tool for processing YAML,
 JSON, XML, CSV, TOML and properties files. It uses a jq-like syntax for
 querying, transforming and updating structured data files.
 .
 This package provides the Go implementation of yq by Mike Farah and replaces
 the Python-based yq package.
